  _packageCreatureName: Inpup
  _packageCreatureDescription: Inpups are the perfect companion for most occasions.
    Their adaptability with any tools with the outlet on their snout allows them
    to help out with most tasks.
  _packageCreaturePersonality: Inpups are playful creatures. You can usually find
    them sticking something into their outlet snouts and playing around with it.
  _packageCreatureWeight: 10
  _packageCreatureLength: 40
  _packageCreatureAbilityName: Adaptability
  _packageCreatureAbilityDescription: Using the plug on the end of its snout, Inpup
    can use most tools to perform actions with them.
